## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="93b1a-118">池越大，系统允许的活动峰值就越大，但工作集也会随之增大。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93b1a-118">Larger pool sizes make the system more tolerant to activity spikes at the cost of a larger working set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93b1a-119">`WebMessageEncodingElement` 可配置能够读取和编写纯文本 XML、JSON 和原始二进制文件的复合编码器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93b1a-119">The `WebMessageEncodingElement` configures a composite encoder that is capable of reading and writing plain-text XML, JSON, and raw binary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93b1a-120">此编码器由三个独立的编码器组成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93b1a-120">This encoder is composed of three separate encoders.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93b1a-121">此设置会影响每个独立编码器的最大读取器数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93b1a-121">This setting affects the maximum number of readers for each individual encoder.</span></span>  
  
   
  
